Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD2DBE0&\bord0}叱られるって思い込む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD2DBE0&\bord0}何か願った　それだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HB6D7E1&\3a&H64&\blur1}ぶつかってばかり傷だらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HEAEBE1&\bord0}だけど走った地球の上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:26.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H3C5048&\3a&H64&\blur2}どうしたくてこうしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HC2AFE0&}理由を探すくせがある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:38.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}人に説明出来るような　言葉に直ってたまるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:41.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an2}とても素晴らしい日になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:45.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H282524&\3c&H8D8B89&\3a&H64&\blur2\an2}怖がりながらも選んだ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H24292C&\3c&HB7CDD0&\3a&H64&\blur2\an2}君の行きたい場所を目指す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H232122&\bord0\an2}太陽は今日のためにあった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:03:00.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\an2}心が宝石を生む度に 高く浮かべて名前付けた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:07.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\bord0\an2}強くなくたって面白い 涙と笑った最初の日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:57.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD8CEBB&\blur2\3c&H21130C&}聽到馬戲團的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H7F6D65&\bord0}大家都歡喜雀躍加快著腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:04.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HDEBFA8&\blur2\3c&H87634E&}我也跟著要跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HFDF7F1&\bord0}儘管自己並沒有門票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD2DBE0&\bord0}滿以為又要被訓斥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HD2DBE0&\bord0}默默地祈禱 僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HB6D7E1&\3a&H64&\blur1}我們總是碰撞傷痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&HEAEBE1&\bord0}仍在奔跑在地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:26.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H3C5048&\3a&H64&\blur2}假如這樣假如那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HC2AFE0&}總是為自己尋找藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:38.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}編造一些能向別人說明的空話 又有什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:41.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\an8}日子會是無限美好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:45.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H282524&\3c&H8D8B89&\3a&H64&\blur2\an8}這是我們懷著恐懼依然選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H24292C&\3c&HB7CDD0&\3a&H64&\blur2\an8}我們向著你想去的地方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H232122&\bord0\an8}太陽就是為了今天而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:03:00.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\an8}每當心中萌生出寶石 就為它起一個最深刻的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:07.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\bord0\an8}即使不強大也是樂趣依舊 一如充滿淚水和歡笑的最初的日子
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什…什…什麼東西啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 不管是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要來妨礙我 我可不會客氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海德拉！將牠打下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 巴哈姆特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…海德拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊 趕緊收拾牠！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不夠！趕緊繼續的射！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒還手就被滅了 真是虛有其表啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼可能！怎麼可能！怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是真的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻星晶獸到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤…撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員趕緊回到船上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須馬上回帝都彙報！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是露莉亞的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很駭人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞 這條龍到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠是巴哈姆特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠借給我們了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借給我們了力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 將力量借給了我和古蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點兒！古蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼端…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是天空的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於抵達了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在星之島伊斯塔爾西亞等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這地方偷懶個啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你又在讀你老爸寄來的信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風之島 火之島 巨大的龍呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有神奇力量的星之民等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到在天空的另一端有著這樣的冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就特別興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要成為騎空士到達那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要到星之島 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 完全不死心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞隆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那玩意兒只是個童話故事罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信上都寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書上也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否真的存在都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是童話故事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定就是別人編造出來的故事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要信到什麼時候啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是編的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星之島絕對存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為老爸在那裡等著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成為像老爸一樣的騎空士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後前往星之島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在森林都能迷路的古蘭肯定到不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是碰巧搞錯了路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算在天空中也迷路嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不行就不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行不行 絕對不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}行行行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們兩個！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吵架！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再吵不給你們點心吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要抱怨的話忙完後再抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然知道你收到信很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但過於沉迷了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你還是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會肯定會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到了那個時候 你就去親眼確認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會在我的家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能醒來 真是太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的傷口也完全癒合了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上有沒有地方痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如肚子或者腦袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼奇怪的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 別讓俺擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}什麼啊 趕緊住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 碧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國的那些傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你暫時不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國軍已經撤離這座島了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以撤退時的形勢來看 應該沒法馬上回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活該！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村裡的人們也沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 村裡似乎沒有受害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受了重傷的人只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他雖然受了致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是因為魔法啥的而治癒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…魔法沒辦法讓死者復生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那麼 到底是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是露莉亞的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞的…力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 古蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事必須告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你做好覺悟聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國在星晶的研究方面投入了很大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想以此來擴大版圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其研究的最高機密就是露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算帝國拿出了全部的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法解析露莉亞所擁有的大部分力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帶著長久以來被監禁的露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看無限延伸的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞的力量是星晶之力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可以控制星之民的遺物——星晶獸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻黑龍應該是碰巧沉睡在這座島上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠被露莉亞的力量喚醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契機應該是沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本星晶獸只聽從星之民的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說這位小姐姐是傳說中的星之民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我想應該不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說星之民在幾百年前就行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有任何子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼她到底是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞沒有被帝國囚禁前的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道自己是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道為什麼會擁有這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想拯救古蘭的那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道 我還有能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將我的生命分享給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此古蘭取回了生命的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們卻沒辦法分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在跟露莉亞共用一個生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換句話來說 你們現在是彼此相互扶持的半身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果相隔太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互間的扶持將會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個人都會喪命的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將一半的生命給了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做的也就僅此而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們打算在帝國回來之前離開這座島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 也希望你能與我們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了擺脫追捕 這將會是一段永無止境的旅程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉 將你捲了進來 古蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得有客人來 必須搞得隆重些才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個已經喝起來了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你們沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好遲啊 古蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好豐盛的大餐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝大家的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次為你們帶來了大麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好了 過來 過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先從乾杯開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次帝國襲擊的原因在於我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再次向大家表示歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們只是被帝國追捕而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭也平安無事 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…不能給你們再添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們打算明天離開這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠趕的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後關於這趟旅程…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也跟卡塔莉娜她們一起出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉 古蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的死並不是露莉亞和卡塔莉娜的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 露莉亞卻為我使用了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因此…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握住了你伸過來的雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要活下去的…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒辦法和你分開讓我很驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但對我來說不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很久以前就做好去旅行的覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一個想要到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父親在那裡等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道它在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我早就決定用我自己的雙眼親自去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請帶上我去旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會跟著去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路途上同伴越多越穩當不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起踏上無盡的天空之旅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便也當成是去尋找拯救你們的方法的旅程如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣闊的天空中一定會存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了 我想到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個找到這個方法的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星之島！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是和星之力相關的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只要能到達那裡 總會找到解決辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞過去的記憶也一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星之島？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會突然說起這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種童話故事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成為像爸爸那樣的騎空士前往星之島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想實現這個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將穿越瘴流域離開范特格蘭德空域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:15.42,Default,NTP,400,0,0,,{\fs30}Phantagrande
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴流域？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個魔物四處徘徊的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要去那麼危險的地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說星之島在瘴流域以外更遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭是我們的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想盡可能地幫助他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺也會跟著去的 不用擔心啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜥蜴同行會派上用場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺不是蜥蜴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼危險的旅程 你是認真的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們很清楚這次旅程的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且如果跟著你們的話 古蘭不也會被那些傢伙追嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想請他們帶我走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次都這樣不經過大腦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底…你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭一直都在考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直在等待這種機會的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從他收到信的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直在鍛煉自己的劍術也是為了這一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村裡人都懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 嚇了你一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…知道的 你做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果見到了你的老爸 你還會回到這座島上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我們還沒乾杯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去旅行的話就得先填飽肚子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這麼多！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦 多吃點兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜 古蘭就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來證明這不是一個虛構的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…騎空艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 雖然是小型艇 但性能很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天白雲朵朵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個啟程的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你父親送行的時候也是這樣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去親眼看看那傢伙所看到的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位也保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了 降下來的時候是這樣操作來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是要下降 而是要升空好嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視野…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們進入了雲層！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之趕緊爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不趕緊爬升的話我們就會撞到島的邊緣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上升吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來天空如此寬廣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達這個高度的話應該沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來那麼小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨不得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 因為我承諾過肯定會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以出發吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往父親那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往星之島 伊斯塔爾西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:21:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(PV)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請使用我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.34,0:23:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給你的話 一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露莉亞的…力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,200,,{\fnFZDaBiaoSong-B06\bord0\fad(300,0)}與你一起編寫 天空的故事——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初始之龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗火焰之子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝之名為
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈姆特！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一個想要到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.87,0:24:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我好的人…這次換做我來保護他們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.90,0:24:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路途上同伴越多越穩當不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是露莉亞的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.70,0:24:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好 我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是小孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.60,0:24:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個能獨當一面的魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.81,0:24:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬事屋萬事包搞定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.27,0:24:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.15,0:24:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦 那孩子是認真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起踏上無盡的天空之旅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.22,0:24:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Granblue Fantasy The Animation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.80,0:24:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2017年4月開始播放
